prompt:
This endpoint takes ~8s to render a page of 200 invoices and the DB dashboard shows thousands of tiny queries. What's wrong and how do I fix it? (TypeORM)

```ts
const invoices = await invoiceRepo.find({ where: { status: 'open' }, take: 200 });
for (const inv of invoices) {
  inv.customer = await customerRepo.findOne({ where: { id: inv.customerId } });
  inv.lines = await lineRepo.find({ where: { invoiceId: inv.id } });
}
return invoices;
```
